📊 SuperMarket Sales Performance Dashboard (Excel Project)

🔹 Project Overview

This project showcases my ability to use Excel for data analysis and dashboard creation. I worked with a retail sales dataset to analyze business performance and present key insights through an interactive dashboard.

It reflects how I approach real-world data—cleaning it, analyzing it, and turning it into meaningful insights.

🔹 Objective

The goal of this project is to:

Analyze sales and profit trends over time
Identify top and underperforming products
Compare performance across different regions
Build a clear and interactive dashboard for decision-making

🔹 Dataset Description

The dataset used is a Supermarket Sales dataset from Kaggle, containing transactional retail data such as:

Order Date
Product & Category
Region / City
Sales
Profit
Quantity

This dataset represents typical retail business operations and is useful for performance analysis.

🔹 Tools & Skills Used
Microsoft Excel
Data Cleaning & Preparation
Pivot Tables
Data Visualization (Charts)
Slicers for Interactivity
Excel Formulas

🔹 Data Preparation

To ensure accurate analysis, I:
Removed duplicate records
Handled missing values
Standardized date formats
Created additional columns:
Month
Year
Month-Year
Profit Margin

🔹 Analysis Performed
Using Excel, I analyzed the data to answer key business questions:

How are sales trending over time?
Which regions are the most profitable?
Which products contribute the most to revenue?
Which products are underperforming?

🔹 Dashboard Features

The final dashboard includes:
KPI Metrics
Total Sales
Total Profit
Profit Margin
Visualizations
Sales trend over time
Profit by region
Top-performing products
Interactive Filters
Region
Category
Year

🔹 End Goal
The goal of this project is to demonstrate how raw data can be transformed into clear, actionable insights using Excel, and how dashboards can support business decisions.

🔹 Key Takeaways

This project highlights my ability to:

Work with raw datasets and prepare them for analysis
Use Pivot Tables to extract insights
Build clean and interactive dashboards
Present data in a way that supports decision-making
